name: Billy the Cat: Recherche M. Hubert désespérément

description: Imagine if...Peter Bishop was a superhero, billionaire playboy by day, costumed vigilante by night! With the help of the always-faithful Walter and Police Chief Commissioner Broyles--The Pattern takes on Fringe incidents throughout Boston City. When his arch-nemesis Mr. ZFT escapes from prison, steals a universe-crossing device, and kidnaps a young Olivia Dunham, will our Cortexiphan Crusader have finally met his match?
name: Imagine If...Peter Was A Superhero

description: In this alternate reality, we find Peter, Olivia, Walter and Astrid embroiled in a high-tech art heist...but not as the crime fighting FBI agents we're used to--now they're the criminals!
name: Imagine If...Our Fringe Team Were Criminals!

description: "Ghost Writer" is a two-part story written by acclaimed animation and comic book creator Jhonen Vasquez and drawn by award-winning comic artist Becky Cloonan. When Nina Sharp's arm appears to be acting on its own, it may have a connection to experiments conducted by Walter Bishop and William Bell back in the 1970s. Continued in BEYOND THE FRINGE Chapter 6A.
name: Ghost Writer Part 1

description: Imagine If...Fringe was in space! In an alternate future where the Earth has been destroyed, we find Walter, newly unfrozen from cryogenic sleep, leading a spaceship of surviving humans through the universe, searching for another planet to call home.
name: Imagine If...Walter Outlived the Earth

description: The conclusion to a two-part story written by acclaimed animation and comic book creator Jhonen Vasquez, and drawn by award-winning comic artist Becky Cloonan. Learn how Nina Sharp lost her arm in an inter-dimensional accident, and how Walter Bishop and William Bell used their brilliant minds to help her, even from beyond the grave.
name: Ghost Writer Part 2

description: In this, our final view of a parallel Fringe universe, we go back to the mid-60s when Walter Bishop, William Bell, and Nina Sharp were just starting their scientific endeavors at Harvard. When an ambitious experiment almost proves deadly, it scares Walter enough to quit science and become a rock star--in Violet Sedan Chair! But will a life in a rock band make him happy?
name: Imagine if...Walter was in Violet Sedan Chair
